PARKING LOTS BY DOME


This pack add small full functional parking lots of different shapes and type to the game, they can be used to help at detailing any kind of build!

Snap them directly to roads or add it to your build and then connect them by invisible roads.

This pack includes:

3x Normal Parking Lots - for 1, 2 and 3 vehicles;

3x Diagonal Parking Lots - for 1, 2 and 3 vehicles;

3x Disabled Parking Lots - fpr 1, 2 and 3 vehicles;

3x Invisible Parking Lots - for 1, 2 and 3 vehicles;

2x Double Parking Lots - for 2 and 4 vehicles;

1x Sideways Parking lot - just for 1 vehicle;

4x Motorbike Parking lot - for 1, 2, 3 and 4 vehicles.

KNOWN ISSUES

These lots have an invisible road build in them, put them too close to each other, in any direction, may cause a malfunction. 
If this occurs, try to change the type of connection (one lane road, one way roads or without pedestrian path). 
If you're familiar with Gizmos - Pathfinding option, you can see if they work properly or not, functional lot will have a black arrows connection to paths, non-functional ones will have a red dot in the center.
